  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with an incisional hernia in the midline and controls with an intact abdominal wall
      are examined twice with one week apart, in order to establish the test-retest reliability and
      internal and external validity of the Goodstrength trunk dynamometer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
